# 🖥️ Simulation

This folder contains instructions and configuration files for setting up the Bumblebee simulator.

The simulator runs on **Ubuntu 20.04** using ROS Noetic and Gazebo.

For the full setup guide:
👉 **[Bumblebee Students Wiki](https://github.com/ermoluk/bumblebee-students/wiki)**

## Quick Start

```bash
# Launch the simulator
roslaunch bumblebee_simulation simulator.launch
```
